<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bem-vindo à Axis</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #1a1a1a;
            --accent-color: #c5a059; /* Tom dourado/bronze para elegância */
            --text-color: #333;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .welcome-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .welcome-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .logo-area {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .logo-placeholder {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .logo-placeholder span {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        .divider {
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .footer-text {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="welcome-card">
        <div class="logo-area">
            <div class="logo-placeholder">AX<span>IS</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h1>Seja bem-vindo(a)</h1>
        
        <p>
            É um prazer ter você conosco. Na <strong>Axis Estratégia Digital</strong>, transformamos visão em presença digital de alto impacto. Prepare-se para elevar o seu posicionamento.
        </p>

        <a href="#" class="btn">Começar Jornada</a>

        <div class="footer-text">
            ESTRATÉGIA DIGITAL • DESIGN • PERFORMANCE
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>